accessibility.text: Straightforward self segmentation is important for motivating potential candidates to apply. Directing uncertain candidates to explore and learn more by scrolling down encourages them to find a path to jobs relevant to them. The only other action available to candidates is the search bar that directs candidates more certain of what they are looking for to self segment to immediately begin searching. The whole process of searching is designed to streamline the process of finding the right job once the candidate is certain of what they are looking for. Search is interrogated later on in the presentation.
